    Scope and Contents
Files includes daily and hourly operation schedules and promo copy.  Included are music logs, daily program schedules of programs played and scheduled time slots.  Scripts for promotional announcements. A  brochure explaining how patrons may support the station is included. Files include information from part of 1977 to Spring of 1991.  
  
